{"tid":2140397,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"報告詳列人道救援者受侵犯  林鄭PK鄧縱容警暴 英跨黨派促制裁","createTime":"2020-08-05T03:40:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-05T04:19:15.000Z","uid":25558,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b253ba2a1590b57bec9bf93fc27de7b11f4a1b05","tid":2140397,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T03:40:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200805/PADMGIQILGRTZQ4BL7D4XPDO64/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200805%2FPADMGIQILGRTZQ4BL7D4XPDO64%2F&d=Iz1eZ%2FSDqTYQUikxH7ZeaoDCThP5nbHt%2BrJRLkanJ30%3D&h=96b7e609\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200805%2FPADMGIQILGRTZQ4BL7D4XPDO64%2F&h=78dde90d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200805/PADMGIQILGRTZQ4BL7D4XPDO64/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n報告詳列人道救援者受侵犯 <br />\n林鄭PK鄧縱容警暴 英跨黨派促制裁<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】過去一年多以來，香港警方在特首林鄭月娥包庇下持續作出反人類暴行，最新證據是英國國會跨黨派香港小組（APPG）的調查報告。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n英國國會跨黨派香港小組於今年3月展開調查，成員收集了1,000份證據，並邀請10名主要證人出席聽證會，當中包括醫護人員、記者、人道主義工作者、學者和前警員。。。。。。。。。。。。。亦影響為受傷示威者提供醫療援助的能力。<br />\n<br />\n整份長達80頁的報告分為多個部份，。。。。。。。。。。。。該急救員被要求蹲低，面向牆壁，其中有警員喝罵指「乜X嘢救護啊」，並指其用以急救的剪刀為危險武器。<br />\n<br />\n報告指出，《中英聯合聲明》中第3條第5款保障港人的權利和自由，故任何違反這些權利的行為，亦是違反《聲明》中的標準和要求。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/dCdW1H56_vycx67tH9vnDCC926I=/640x480/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LL2EMXGC2XUDGN5CO4OZQ7FU3M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FdCdW1H56_vycx67tH9vnDCC926I%3D%2F640x480%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLL2EMXGC2XUDGN5CO4OZQ7FU3M.jpg&h=1fded6f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n英國國會小組建議制裁縱容警暴的港府高級官員，包括林鄭月娥（左）和鄧炳強。<br />\n倡BNO入籍政策排除撐警者<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：被捕反綁坐地 醫生：警想侮辱醫護<br />\n<br />\n報告建議英國制裁容許警暴的高級官員，不限於行政長官林鄭月娥和警務處長。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小組聯席主席班奈特女男爵（Natalie Bennett）指，港版國安法案實施後，港人在街頭活動中須拿白紙示威，亦有人因社交媒體的貼文而被捕，形容香港正面對「非常艱巨及不穩定」的情況，非常欣賞港人仍然勇敢抗爭。<br />\n<br />\n25歲的義務急救員David（化名）認同報告結論，早於2014年雨傘運動中已以急救員身份支援的他認為，當年警察仍會尊重、不會阻撓他們，甚至會主動讓路予他們急救傷者。但至反送中運動，警察對急救員的態度明顯惡化，甚至有施暴和濫捕行為。<br />\n<br />\nDavid的隊友也曾遭胡椒彈和催淚彈擊中受傷，他為香港人權大大倒退感到可悲：「理論上我哋係中立嘅第三者角色，但警察明顯當我哋係敵人，佢哋已經墮落成極權工具。」但他表明運動一日未完，仍會以急救員身份走上現場：「雖然抗爭嘅空間越來越少，但唔想見到有人受傷，做得幾多得幾多。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/9cqOFJGAFfNalkZB3f-XN_h7Pfk=/1417x398/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OCBS5CPLL6FAID4BSKQ6PYMSCQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F9cqOFJGAFfNalkZB3f-XN_h7Pfk%3D%2F1417x398%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOCBS5CPLL6FAID4BSKQ6PYMSCQ.gif&h=2db578ec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e403e39a71c63ae8b2c6bc09c6af14195eba3758","tid":2140397,"uid":75300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T03:43:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8051ab6eb5b3d365dc784484548b9fd12e58ba64","tid":2140397,"uid":38518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T03:48:13.000Z","msg":"應該連坐，否則柒婆不痛不癢"},{"pid":"641307a4bf5158f3f7cee1ea774cbb53eee378d7","tid":2140397,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T03:48:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AgaTU5R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAgaTU5R.jpg&h=ad80ccb2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2df9a72d1032c297bd564c5f4ae9bbd82efdfe92","tid":2140397,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T03:49:22.000Z","msg":"仲有盧偉聰同劉業成呀"},{"pid":"19495383ea961e72ac12bb775473ada081abd24d","tid":2140397,"uid":75765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"64